**Scapegoat Defense** | Attribute
__Basics__
A technical attribute used by the scapegoat for the lynch defense it grants its attacker.

__Formalized__
Starting: Target @ThisAttr->Source
Starting: Protect @Self from `Lynches` through Active Defense (~UntilUseAttribute)
On Active Defense: Lynch @ThisAttr->Source
On @Target Death: Remove @ThisAttr from @Self
